OL,3,CPeople warned to boil water as disease
OL,4,Ccases confirmed
OL,6,FPeople living in parts of Devon are
OL,7,Fbeing warned to boil tap water after
OL,8,Fmultiple cases of cryptosporidium were
OL,9,Fconfirmed.
OL,11,FThe UK Health Security Agency has
OL,12,Fconfirmed 16 cases of the parasite,
OL,13,Fwhich causes a diarrhoea-type illness,
OL,14,Fin the Brixham area.
OL,16,FThere have been a further 70 reported
OL,17,Fcases of vomiting and diarrhoea.
