OL,6,FThe government says the disease is
OL,7,F"predominantly waterborne" and
OL,8,Finfections can be caused by drinking
OL,9,Fcontaminated water.
OL,11,FSouth West Water has found small
OL,12,Ftraces of cryptosporidium in part of
OL,13,Fits network. As a result, a boil water
OL,14,Fnotice has been issued for people
OL,15,Fliving in the Alston and Hillhead area
OL,16,Fof Brixton.
