OL,6,FThe firm says the water is safe for
OL,7,Fwashing and bathing but people should
OL,8,Fnot drink it, use it to prepare food
OL,9,For to brush their teeth without
OL,10,Fboiling it first.
OL,12,FBoiled water can be stored in a
OL,13,Fcovered container in the fridge for 24
OL,14,Fhours. Bottled water stations are also
OL,15,Fdue to be set up.
OL,17,FWater warning issued to residents in
OL,18,FBrixham - what advice is being given?
OL,20,FWater is safe for washing, bathing and
OL,21,Fflushing the toilet as normal.
