OL,6,FWhat are the symptoms of
OL,7,Fcryptosporidium infection?
OL,9,FCryptosporidium is a parasite found in
OL,10,Flakes, streams and rivers, untreated
OL,11,Fdrinking water and sometimes in
OL,12,Fswimming pools.
OL,14,FThe main symptoms of cryptosporidium
OL,15,Finfection are:
OL,17,FSymptoms may only last a couple of
OL,18,Fdays but can continue for up to three
OL,19,For four weeks. It can affect people
OL,20,Fwith weak immune systems for much
OL,21,Flonger.
