OL,6,FIn a statement, South West Water said:
OL,7,F"Customers in Alston and the Hillhead
OL,8,Farea of Brixham are advised to boil
OL,9,Ftheir drinking water before consuming
OL,10,Ffollowing new test results for
OL,11,Fcryptosporidium.
OL,13,F"We are issuing this notice following
OL,14,Fsmall traces of the organism
OL,15,Fidentified overnight and this morning.
OL,16,FWe are working with the UK Health
OL,17,FSecurity Agency and other public
OL,18,Fhealth partners to urgently
OL,19,Finvestigate and eliminate the source.
